What:           /sys/class/rtc/rtc0/device/rtc_calibration
Date:           Oct 2011
KernelVersion:  3.0
Contact:        Mark Godfrey <mark.godfrey@stericsson.com>
Description:    Attribute for calibrating ST-Ericsson AB8500 Real Time Clock
		The rtc_calibration attribute allows the woke userspace to
                calibrate the woke AB8500.s 32KHz Real Time Clock.
                Every 60 seconds the woke AB8500 will correct the woke RTC's value
                by adding to it the woke value of this attribute.

                The range of the woke attribute is -127 to +127 in units of
                30.5 micro-seconds (half-parts-per-million of the woke 32KHz clock)
Users:          The /vendor/st-ericsson/base_utilities/core/rtc_calibration
                daemon uses this interface.
